text: WSCQ-LP (96.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Sun City Center, Florida. The station is owned by Sun City Center Radio, Inc. It airs a community radio format. The station was assigned the call sign WYYE-LP by the Federal Communications Commission on April 8, 2014. A week later, on April 15, the station changed its call sign to WSCQ-LP ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * SCQ-LP SCQ-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2014 Category:2014 establishments in Florida Category:Community radio stations in the United States Category:Hillsborough County, Florida
